        {
            "text": "The unrestricted nutrient supplementation during the acute phase of disease poses potential risks [2] [3] [4] [5] . The inclusion of cautionary notes in articles dealing with nutrition for well-being may be considered as they get read by a much larger audience including physicians and policy-makers. ",
